# GoMonitor

# Description:

GoMonitor is a lightway way to monitor deployed docker containers. GoMonitor uses the Golang Docker API to recieve notifcations on the state of deployed containers.
Owners of containers can receive notifcations via email.

# Features:

- Notifies email recipients of issues with deployed containers
- Custom actions allowing you to choose what to monitor
- Container logs sent to owner via email attachment

# License

This project is open source, feel free to use this code openly.

# Support and Feedback

If you encounter any issues or have suggestions for improving GoMonitor, please feel free to open an issue on GitHub. Your feedback is valuable.
